---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Home">

  <div class="hero">
    <img src="/hero.jpg" alt="Kuniyoshi — Fording of the Uji River, 1184" class="hero-img" />
    <div class="hero-overlay">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <p class="hero-kicker">A Setting for Savage Worlds Adventure Edition</p>
        <h1 class="hero-title">Savage Bushido</h1>
        <p class="hero-tagline">Steel and honor in warring-states Nippon</p>
        <div class="hero-buttons">
          <a href="/rules" class="btn-primary">Read the Rules</a>
          <a href="/about" class="btn-secondary">About the Game</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="intro">
    <div class="intro-text">
      <p>The blade catches the afternoon light as it clears the scabbard. Across the garden, the Daimyo's tea cup is halfway to his lips. Neither man speaks.</p>
      <p>Welcome to Nippon — a world of extraordinary beauty and extraordinary violence, where the way you carry a sword and the way you pour tea are equally martial arts.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">⚔</div>
        <h2>Bugei — The Martial Arts</h2>
        <p>A three-tier system of martial Edges — Category Omote, Specialist, and Okuden secret techniques — built on real teacher relationships in play.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">巻</div>
        <h2>On — The Honor Score</h2>
        <p>A 1–20 honor score that follows your character everywhere, shapes every social roll, and changes through every decision you make.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">火</div>
        <h2>Three Arcane Traditions</h2>
        <p>Shugendo elemental sorcery, Buddhist miracles, and Shinto Kami-granted powers — each with distinct mechanics, costs, and social position.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">鳥</div>
        <h2>A Living World</h2>
        <p>The Shikken tightens his grip. Yorike returns from war. The Ryojii-Wada conflict spreads. Nippon does not wait for the players to act.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta">
      <a href="/rules/chapter-one" class="btn-primary">Start Reading — Chapter One</a>
      <a href="/tools" class="btn-secondary">Player Tools</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="playtest-banner">
  <p>Running a playtest session? <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSej4cuMaQM1e78kpwGZSaEtTIs0PfL57fetoNx30h5lTxhk3w/viewform" target="_blank">Submit your feedback →</a></p>
</div>

</Layout>

<style>
  :global(main) { padding: 0 !important; }

  .hero {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 520px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 20%;
    display: block;
  }

  .hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to right,
      rgba(26, 18, 8, 0.88) 0%,
      rgba(26, 18, 8, 0.65) 50%,
      rgba(26, 18, 8, 0.2) 100%
    );
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero-content {
    padding: 3rem 4rem;
    max-width: 540px;
  }

  .hero-kicker {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: #c4a96b;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #f5f0e3;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #c4a96b;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
  }

  .hero-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #8b1a1a;
    color: #f5f0e3;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: #b8902a; color: #1a1208; }

  .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-block;
    background: transparent;
    color: #f5f0e3;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    border: 1px solid rgba(196, 169, 107, 0.5);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover { background: rgba(196, 169, 107, 0.15); border-color: #c4a96b; }

  .intro {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .intro-text {
    border-left: 3px solid #c4a96b;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .intro-text p {
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #3d2b10;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .feature-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .feature {
    background: #ede5cc;
    border: 1px solid #c4a96b;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #8b1a1a;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .feature h2 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #8b1a1a;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
  }

  .feature p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #3d2b10;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #c4a96b;
  }

  .cta .btn-secondary {
    color: #3d2b10;
    border-color: #c4a96b;
  }
  .cta .btn-secondary:hover { background: #e0d5b8; }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .hero { height: 400px; }
    .hero-content { padding: 2rem; }
    .hero-title { font-size: 2.5rem; }
    .feature-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .cta { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
  }
  .playtest-banner {
  margin-top: 3rem;
  padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
  background: #ede5cc;
  border: 1px solid #c4a96b;
  border-left: 4px solid #8b1a1a;
  border-radius: 4px;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: #3d2b10;
}

.playtest-banner a {
  color: #8b1a1a;
  font-weight: bold;
  text-decoration: none;
}

.playtest-banner a:hover {
  color: #b8902a;
}
</style>
